item.description: Join Sue Nordemo for an intro to Self Hypnosis for stress management! Learn some of the myths and facts about hypnosis and how it works, what imprinting is and how it effects our lives and creates positive change in your life - empowering you with physical, spiritual and emotional well-being and allowing you to create the life you choose. Hypnosis and self-hypnosis is safe, effective and easy to learn. Expect to have fun, to learn a lot and to let go fo some stress!
